Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]] (Geometry), [[tsazano]] (Square) chiumbwa chine mativi mana ose akaenzana negonya ina dzose dzakaenzana. Tsazano riri mumupanda wegonyaina.

==Pimamuganhu neNharaunda==

[[Pimamuganhu]] ye[[tsazano]] rine mativi akareba nhambwe '''K''' inowanikwa ne[[tsazaniso]] inoti:  

'''Pimamuganhu, P  =  4.K''',

uye [[Nharaunda]] ye[[tsazano]] inowanikwa netsazaniso inoti:

'''Nharaunda, A  =  K<sup>2</sup>'''

==Zvifaniro zveTsazano==

[[Tsazano]] iri mumupanda we[[gonyaina tsazamativi]] ne[[gonyaina tsazamakonya]], saka zvinoreva kuti ine zvose [[zvifaniro]] (properties) zviumbwa zviviri izvi; sokuti:

* [[Danhamakonya]] mbiri dzinochekana ne[[gonya]] re 90<sup>o</sup> uye dzinochekana kuita zvikamu zviviri zvakaenzana.
* Danhamakonya dzetsazano dzinocheka makonya muzvikamu zviviri zvakaenzana.
* Mativi akatarisana etsazano akaenzana uye akati [[sambamba]].
* Danhamakonya mbiri dzetsazano dzakaenzana
* Makonya ose ari mana etsazano akaenza ari 90<sup>o</sup>

